@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
[*] --> Cancelled
Cancelled --> Shipped : update
Shipped --> Created : confirm
Shipped : entry / log post
Created --> Rejected : process
Rejected --> OnHold : cancel
Rejected : entry / log post
Cancelled --> OnHold : revert
OnHold --> [*]
@enduml